Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Latitude coordinate of the property location in decimal degrees
Check Description: Ensures latitude is present (no NULL values). Critical for property geolocation and mapping.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(LATITUDE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.LATITUDE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Latitude coordinate of the property location in decimal degrees
Check Description: Validates latitude is within valid geographic range [-90, 90] and not a default zero value.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(LATITUDE) = 0:
      # Valid range check
      valid min: -90
      valid max: 90
      # Block default zero values
      invalid values: [0, 0.0, 0.000]
      name: "[Critical] Property.LATITUDE — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Longitude coordinate of the property location in decimal degrees
Check Description: Ensures longitude is present (no NULL values). Critical for property geolocation and mapping.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(LONGITUDE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.LONGITUDE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Longitude coordinate of the property location in decimal degrees
Check Description: Validates longitude is within valid geographic range [-180, 180] and not a default zero value.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(LONGITUDE) = 0:
      # Valid range check
      valid min: -180
      valid max: 180
      # Block default zero values
      invalid values: [0, 0.0, 0.000]
      name: "[Critical] Property.LONGITUDE — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Postal or ZIP code of the property location
Check Description: Ensures postal code is present for all properties. Required for address validation and mail delivery.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(POSTAL_CODE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.POSTAL_CODE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Postal or ZIP code of the property location
Check Description: Validates postal code format is not empty string or placeholder values.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(POSTAL_CODE) = 0:
      invalid values: ['', 'N/A', 'NULL', 'UNKNOWN', '00000']
      name: "[Major] Property.POSTAL_CODE — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Name of the city where the property is located
Check Description: Ensures city name is present for all properties. Critical for location identification and reporting.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(CITY_NAME) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.CITY_NAME — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Unique identifier code for the property building
Check Description: Ensures building code is present. This is the primary identifier for properties.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(PROPERTY_BUILDING_CODE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.PROPERTY_BUILDING_CODE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Unique identifier code for the property building
Check Description: Ensures building codes are unique across all properties. Duplicates would indicate data quality issues.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - duplicate_count(PROPERTY_BUILDING_CODE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.PROPERTY_BUILDING_CODE — Uniqueness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Net rentable area of the property available for lease
Check Description: Validates net rentable area is positive and within reasonable range. Zero or negative values indicate data errors.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(NET_RENTABLE_AREA) = 0:
      valid min: 0.01
      valid max: 10000000
      invalid values: [0, 0.0, -1]
      name: "[Major] Property.NET_RENTABLE_AREA — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Description of the space availability status
Check Description: Validates status values are from the approved list of availability statuses.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_DESC) = 0:
      valid values: ['Available', 'Occupied', 'Under Construction', 'Reserved', 'Maintenance']
      name: "[Major] Property.SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_DESC — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: First line of the property address
Check Description: Ensures primary address line is present. Required for property identification and communication.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(ADDRESS_LINE1) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.ADDRESS_LINE1 — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Type or classification of the property (e.g., Office, Retail, Industrial)
Check Description: Ensures property type is specified for all properties. Required for property classification and reporting.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(PROPERTY_TYPE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.PROPERTY_TYPE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Primary market or region where the property is located
Check Description: Ensures market classification is present. Critical for market analysis and regional reporting.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(MARKET_NAME) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.MARKET_NAME — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Unique building identifier
Check Description: Ensures building code is present for tracking purposes.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(BUILDING_CODE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.BUILDING_CODE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Year when the property was constructed
Check Description: Validates year built is within reasonable historical range and not in the future.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(YEAR_BUILT) = 0:
      valid min: 1800
      valid max: 2025
      name: "[Major] Property.YEAR_BUILT — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: ZIP or postal code of the property
Check Description: Ensures ZIP code is populated for US properties.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - missing_count(ZIP_CODE) = 0:
      name: "[Critical] Property.ZIP_CODE — Completeness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Total gross leasable area of the property
Check Description: Validates gross leasable area is positive and within expected range.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(GROSS_LEASABLE_AREA) = 0:
      valid min: 1
      valid max: 5000000
      name: "[Major] Property.GROSS_LEASABLE_AREA — Validity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Total surface area available in the property
Check Description: Ensures total available area equals the sum of vacant and occupied areas. Inconsistency indicates calculation errors.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(TOTAL_AVAILABLE_SURFACE_AREA) = 0:
      valid formula: TOTAL_AVAILABLE_SURFACE_AREA >= TOTAL_VACANT_AREA
      name: "[Major] Property.TOTAL_AVAILABLE_SURFACE_AREA — Consistency"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Amount of vacant space in the property
Check Description: Ensures vacant area does not exceed total available area. Logical inconsistency would indicate data error.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(VACANT_AREA) = 0:
      valid formula: VACANT_AREA <= TOTAL_AVAILABLE_SURFACE_AREA
      name: "[Critical] Property.VACANT_AREA — Consistency"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Unit of measure for net rentable area
Check Description: Ensures all area unit of measures are consistent within the same record (NET_RENTABLE_AREA_UOM should match AVAILABLE_SPACE_UOM).
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: NET_RENTABLE_AREA_UOM != AVAILABLE_SPACE_UOM
      name: "[Major] Property.NET_RENTABLE_AREA_UOM — Consistency"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Latitude coordinate of the property location in decimal degrees
Check Description: Cross-validates latitude coordinates against known city locations. Coordinates must align with specified CITY_NAME geography.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: |
        (CITY_NAME = 'Paris' AND (LATITUDE < 48.0 OR LATITUDE > 49.0)) OR
        (CITY_NAME = 'Berlin' AND (LATITUDE < 52.0 OR LATITUDE > 53.0))
      name: "[Major] Property.LATITUDE — Accuracy"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Surrogate key for space availability status
Check Description: Validates that status surrogate key has corresponding description. Orphaned keys indicate broken references.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_SKEY IS NOT NULL AND SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_DESC IS NULL
      name: "[Critical] Property.SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_SKEY — Integrity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Listing representative or agent for the property
Check Description: Ensures listing representative has associated country information. Missing country indicates incomplete relationship.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: LISTINGREP IS NOT NULL AND LISTINGREP_COUNTRIES IS NULL
      name: "[Major] Property.LISTINGREP — Integrity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Date when the associated project was completed
Check Description: Ensures completion dates are not in the future. Future dates indicate data entry errors or incorrect system dates.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: ASSOCIATED_PROJECT_COMPLETION_DATE > CURRENT_DATE()
      name: "[Major] Property.ASSOCIATED_PROJECT_COMPLETION_DATE — Timeliness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Postal or ZIP code of the property location
Check Description: Validates postal code follows standard format patterns for European postal codes.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(POSTAL_CODE) = 0:
      valid regex: ^[A-Z0-9]{3,10}$
      name: "[Major] Property.POSTAL_CODE — Conformity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Name of the street where the property is located
Check Description: Ensures street names follow proper naming conventions without special characters or numbers only.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - invalid_count(STREET_NAME) = 0:
      valid regex: ^[A-Za-z0-9\s\-\.]+$
      invalid regex: ^[0-9]+$
      name: "[Minor] Property.STREET_NAME — Conformity"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Timestamp of when the property record was last updated
Check Description: Ensures property records have been updated within the last 90 days. Stale data may be inaccurate.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: LAST_UPDATED_DATE < DATEADD(day, -90, CURRENT_DATE())
      name: "[Major] Property.LAST_UPDATED_DATE — Timeliness"

Short description of Critical Data Eleme: Current operational status of the property
Check Description: Validates property status aligns with availability status. Inactive properties should not have available spaces.
SODACL Yaml Check Definition:
checks for VW_CE_PROPERTY_DQ:
  - failed rows:
      fail condition: PROPERTY_STATUS = 'Inactive' AND SPACE_AVAILABILITY_STATUS_DESC = 'Available'
      name: "[Critical] Property.PROPERTY_STATUS — Consistency"
